Package: linux-image-4.19.325-xiaomi-pipa
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux kernel for Xiaomi Pad 6 (pipa)
 This package contains the Linux kernel for the Xiaomi Pad 6 device.
 .
 Note: This package only ships the kernel image and modules, you should probably
 look at the linux-bootimage-4.19.325-xiaomi-pipa package for a bootimage suitable
 for Android boot loaders.

Package: linux-bootimage-4.19.325-xiaomi-pipa
Architecture: arm64
Pre-Depends: flash-bootimage (>= 4)
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         linux-image-4.19.325-xiaomi-pipa (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Linux kernel for Xiaomi Pad 6 (pipa) - Android Boot Image
 This package contains the Linux kernel for the Xiaomi Pad 6 device.
 .
 Note: This package ships an Android Boot Image bundled with Halium's
 initramfs.

